stories.title: Pakistan make South Africa sweat for victory
stories.summary:
Sharjah, March 24: South Africa clinched their 14th win on the trot
over Pakistan but not before they were made to sweat in the Sharjah
Cup match at the Sharjah Cricket Stadium here on Friday evening

stories.title: Klusener, Boje star in South African triumph
stories.summary:
The third match of the Coca Cola Cup in Sharjah produced the
first reasonably close finish of the tournament
